<h2>Discover New Reads</h2>
<p>
    The Explore page allows readers to browse and discover books
    outside their personal library. This section serves as a searchable catalog where
    users can find books by title, author, or genre, and quickly add them to their
    own bookshelf.
</p>


<h2>Features</h2>
<p>
    Users can filter results by genre, author, or book title. The search
    bar provides keyword matching, making it simple to locate books of interest.
    Each book preview includes key details such as title, author, average rating,
    and available discussions.
</p>
